dreisoft.tresos.tresosdb.api.model.v2.swcomponenttemplate.components

Interface INvBlockSwComponentType

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IAtomicSwComponentType, IEntity, IIdentifiable, IReferrable, ISwComponentType

    public interface INvBlockSwComponentType
extends IEntity, IAtomicSwComponentType
    INvBlockSwComponentType: Entity class of the tresosDB model.

    The NvBlockSwComponentType defines non volatile data which data can be shared between SwComponentPrototypes. The non volatile data of the NvBlockSwComponentType are accessible via provided and required ports.
